author: @pleaseberational1433
text:
As an ARMY and a Once, I want to first give a message to fellow ARMYs, and then to fellow Onces.
ARMYs, please don't send Twice any hate. Our boys receive hate too, and we know how awful that is. All of us know what it feels like to see our beloved artists being dragged and insulted. So please, don't bring the same pain to another fandom, and one of our sibling fandoms at that.
Onces and ARMYs have a great relationship. So please, don't send Twice any hate. You're being a hypocrite if you do that- sending the message of self love, and telling people that they should appreciate themselves holds no weight if you do this crap. Do you think our boys would like to see you harass another group like this?
Plus, our fandom already has an awful reputation due to the rude behaviour of the minority. Please don't make it worse. üíú

To Onces- I'm sorry for what ARMYs did and I assure you that not all ARMYs are like that. We just have a bigger fandom so there are naturally more toxic fans. Often, trolls pretend to be ARMYs too and it worsens the situation.
I assure you- most ARMYs respect Twice, and are even Onces. I apologize on the behalf of those ARMYs who displayed toxic behavior in this comments section.
I hope this fanwar stops, and that fans learn to respect other groups, and at the very least, learn to refrain from sending hate.
